Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.30,0:00:04.81,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Yuurei-chan and Otama-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.81,0:00:08.49,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind Yuurei-chan, there is always Otama-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.49,0:00:10.94,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The two are always together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.62,0:01:57.97,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:02:01.43,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the whole drifting incident on the ship, I didn't get any work done on the manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:05.31,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry. Please give us one more hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:14.19,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W--Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:19.43,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your manga is too realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:23.16,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go draw me something that I can actually publish next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:26.07,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's easy for you to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.98,0:02:30.74,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't root it in reality this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.74,0:02:32.04,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so it'll probably be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:38.46,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, Imouto-san sure is late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.82,0:02:41.31,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she would be here before six o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:45.05,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:48.92,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sorry, Imouto-san, but can we quickly get start-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:50.56,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:52.32,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Te... T-T-T-T-T-T-Te...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:55.56,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W--Why is Tenma-chan here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:02:58.07,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima-kun, open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:02.20,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakumo couldn't make it so I'm here in her place!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:04.83,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:06.49,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can come in, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:08.86,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Yeah, o--of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:11.41,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:15.70,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I--Itoko's shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.85,0:03:18.99,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:22.30,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's nothing. I just haven't moved around much recently, so I'm getting some exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:24.09,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:26.92,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'm finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:31.09,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. Harima-kun, you live in a pretty nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.09,0:03:33.09,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:38.53,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we have a guest over, Kenji-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.87,0:03:39.40,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:43.08,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:45.55,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N--No way! It must be the television!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:48.70,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The workroom is over that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:52.34,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go make some tea, so wait here for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:53.14,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:57.49,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was way too close for comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.49,0:03:59.83,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would've expected Tenma-chan to show up all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:02.55,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a once in a lifetime opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:05.57,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I--Itoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:08.64,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that on purpose, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:11.74,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I seem to be an annoyance here, so I'm going out for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.34,0:04:18.02,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving the two of you alone. Try your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:25.53,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us alone together...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:32.59,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S--S--S--S--S--Sorry it took so long, Tsuka--Tsuka--Tsuka--Tsukamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:37.74,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! You can see Yagami High School from here! Ah, you can see Yagami Bridge, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:40.67,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it romantic, Harima-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.48,0:04:43.88,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:47.39,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, my heart is racing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:49.07,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It really makes your heart race, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:53.88,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's my first time ever being a manga assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:55.37,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:04:59.81,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I see. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:01.86,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the manuscript?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:03.79,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N--No, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:05.24,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:07.33,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W--Why, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.33,0:05:11.70,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A pro's pride doesn't allow him to show people unfinished works that he's not happy with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:15.66,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That is truly the way of a pro. How admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:20.88,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm just going to clean it up a bit. You go sit down and have some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.16,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:29.01,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. If she sees this, she's going to get everything. My feelings are blatantly obvious in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:33.09,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukamoto, is Imouto-san busy with something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:37.56,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know either, but she just said she was busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.91,0:05:38.91,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:44.53,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. Imouto-san didn't sound like she was busy during the phone call this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:47.33,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, this is the really intellectual Imouto-san we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:50.68,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't she have told me beforehand if something had come up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.44,0:05:53.16,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. With this, I'm probably safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:55.59,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it sure was a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:56.41,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What was?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:58.79,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really can't judge a book by its cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:02.59,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never would have thought that you were drawing manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:04.32,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:07.70,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I was really touched by the last manga you drew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:08.09,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:11.39,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have a better opinion of you now, Harima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:15.40,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I see! This is just like a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:17.73,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima-kun, you're wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:20.32,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.07,0:06:25.31,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be by your side so much that I forced others out of the way just to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:28.29,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:31.79,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, now since it's settled, I have no choice but to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:36.28,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But then again, it's sort of embarrassing to suddenly confess to her since she just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:40.04,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I should indirectly show her some signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:45.18,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:49.21,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'm counting on you to be my assistant, Tsukamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.21,0:06:50.13,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:52.77,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll first give you a brief overview.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.53,0:06:58.18,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a story of a man and a woman who were aboard a cruiser that met with a storm and drifted off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:06:59.01,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:01.16,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the main character.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.16,0:07:02.40,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.46,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the heroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:05.83,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:08.98,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do these two remind of you of anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:10.15,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:12.91,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:15.86,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T--These two are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:17.83,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y--Yes, they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:20.57,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The two who appeared in the last manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:22.83,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is a continuation of that story!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:26.34,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:31.31,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there really is no way but to say it directly to a thick-skulled girl like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:34.43,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tsukamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:35.26,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:40.85,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A work often unwittingly shows the personality and thought process of the author who created it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:43.23,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm? Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:45.04,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This manga is like that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:48.20,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my very soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:51.58,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukamoto, this main character is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.58,0:07:53.86,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, I'm in love with this heroine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:56.15,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And this heroine is none other than--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:07:59.65,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:05.23,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you doing, Kenji-kun? Did you successfully manage to confess to Tsukamoto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:07.66,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:12.44,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, don't call me at the worst possible time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:17.21,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Harima-kun's ring tone is the theme song of "The Three Who Were Slashed?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.21,0:08:17.59,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:19.10,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine is, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:21.77,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,R--Really? What a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:22.73,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:24.78,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:26.07,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What... What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:29.28,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a special episode of The Three today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.77,0:08:32.36,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been showing for over half an hour already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:36.23,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever shall we do?! If we missed the beginning, we wouldn't be able to follow the plot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.13,0:08:39.36,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Yakumo might have recorded it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.36,0:08:40.22,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:41.91,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I'll text her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:51.31,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:54.80,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's Imouto-san for you! She's always prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:59.14,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief. I'll lend it to you later, Harima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:01.27,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:37.80,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you playing outside, Iori?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:48.19,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked Nee-san to go help Harima-san with his manga today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:53.39,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about it for a while, but isn't Harima-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:56.18,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Karasuma show up at Tsukamoto's party?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:10:00.58,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Oh, right. After the party, he came to our house directly instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:01.82,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.90,0:10:06.56,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really pumped now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:13.41,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that Harima-san loves Nee-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:18.42,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Nee-san is completely oblivious to that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:24.06,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted Nee-san to look at Harima-san more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:40.14,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not good to be naughty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:46.87,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:51.38,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san during her middle school years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.91,0:10:59.90,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The best episode has to be episode eighty-nine:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:05.01,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Goodbye, The Three! The Evil Flowers of the Roads of Kamakura in Full Bloom!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:09.95,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah! Mangoku's fight was the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:12.62,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't forget about episode forty-three.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:16.19,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, "Lovesick in Nakasendou While Shouting, 'Come on! Come on!'," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:17.36,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That really brings a tear to your eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:21.44,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah. The guest appearance of Kiku-chan was a really nice touch, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:24.69,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect it, but Tenma-chan really knows her stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:26.87,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're totally compatible with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:28.45,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:31.37,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would have thought that you are a Mangoku fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:34.92,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think that you're a Mangoku fan either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:37.92,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're really compatible with each other, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.22,0:11:40.02,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Te... Tsukamoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:45.38,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're annoying! Stop calling me over and over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.38,0:11:47.69,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Tazawa-kun? This is Mitsui.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:48.64,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:51.02,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound pretty terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:51.86,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:53.31,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:54.34,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:57.14,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please make sure you bring it tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:11:58.86,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:01.90,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The chief has high hopes for you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:03.90,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let us down this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:05.07,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Try your best then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:08.71,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:11.27,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're pressing for the manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:13.00,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When's the deadline?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:13.78,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:15.89,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! We have to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.89,0:12:18.67,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay even if I don't make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:19.30,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:22.69,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Now that you recognized me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:24.93,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I need nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:28.30,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't give up, Harima-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:31.25,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:35.97,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I really want to see your manga appear in Jingama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:36.76,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:40.52,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it has come to this, I'll keep you company until the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:46.03,TL NOTES,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Tenma says "tsukiau," which literally means "to keep company with." However, it can also be interpreted as "to go out on a date."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:42.48,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Date...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:43.40,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Date...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:44.66,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Date...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:46.03,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Date...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:49.00,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You... You'll be with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:51.00,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Let's try our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:54.42,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's give it our best shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:55.96,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:08.00,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.71,0:13:10.63,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed a bit, Nee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.95,0:13:16.26,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This picture book...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:22.43,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will happen after I finish this manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:23.91,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:28.75,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,, We can take our time to work on our relationship after this is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.31,0:13:32.45,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means to go out with someone. Right, Tenma-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.53,0:13:35.00,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tsukamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:35.45,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:38.83,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we finish this before daybreak,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:40.92,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,do you want to go take a bike ride along the coastline?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:43.04,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Coastline?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:47.88,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The view of the morning sunrise above the ocean is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.25,0:13:49.77,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:51.48,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,R--Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:53.09,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Color... Color...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:02.17,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How... How can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:04.17,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to redraw it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:05.74,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to make it in time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:07.32,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:09.65,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all. Thanks a bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:12.18,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what should I do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:15.48,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Uh, well, try sharpening some pencils for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:16.37,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:23.28,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I really understand what this main character is feeling. A one-sided love is really painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:24.25,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:28.69,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Although when the time actually comes, it really is hard to confess your feelings, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.69,0:14:30.09,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That... That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:34.29,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he might think it's fine just to be able to be by her side,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.95,0:14:38.47,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but it won't work out in the end unless he puts it into words.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:39.52,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He needs to be brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:41.65,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Tenma-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:44.63,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you said you'd be with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:46.99,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really unmanly of me to not say it clearly to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:51.02,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to confess properly to Karasuma-kun, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:54.70,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for it, Tenma-chan. I'll properly confess to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.93,0:14:58.63,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:15:00.18,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:02.09,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:11.45,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,am sort of hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.42,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:14.30,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll go order some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:17.02,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cook us something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.34,0:15:18.95,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ehhh?! No, it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:20.47,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so reserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:23.56,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not the point here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:29.88,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where are the condiments?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:31.65,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.25,0:15:34.74,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice. I guess I'll have to ask Itoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:39.48,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like things are heating up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:41.60,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's the condiments you want, then they're under the sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:42.84,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:45.93,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukamoto, the condiments are under the sink...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:48.30,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, how the heck did you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:53.34,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did... Did she put a bug somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:15:59.50,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:00.99,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:07.78,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I pretty much failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:09.65,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:11.61,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.54,0:16:15.07,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I sort of want to wash away the taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:19.12,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's drink something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:27.35,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How in the world is she capable of making something that awful?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.35,0:16:29.01,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost an art.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:30.31,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:33.30,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We both ate the same thing and shared the terrible taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:35.96,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a slight variation of the meaning of "going out!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:40.52,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I made some coffee, Tsukamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:40.93,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.07,0:16:49.61,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:57.75,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Yuurei-chan and Otama-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.61,0:17:01.60,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind Yuurei-chan, there is always Otama-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.11,0:17:04.17,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The two are always together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:06.76,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,During mealtime,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.47,0:17:09.31,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"I don't want any more."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:12.32,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yuurei-chan, don't leave it unfinished."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:15.14,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,During playtime,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.14,0:17:16.82,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"I want this."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:20.77,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yuurei-chan, that's the girl's toy."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:24.17,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when everyone is going on a trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:26.11,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"I want to go that way."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.11,0:17:29.06,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yuurei-chan, everyone is going this way."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:32.62,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"It's fine. I want to go that way."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:37.04,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"If you want to be with everyone, Otama-chan, then you can go with them."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:40.58,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Will you be fine by yourself, Yuurei-chan?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:44.25,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yes, I will be fine by myself."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:47.29,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Otama-chan has a lonely expression on her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:49.99,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But she won't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:53.76,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"I don't care about Otama-chan anymore."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:59.52,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuurei-chan trudged off on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:13.57,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For how long do you plan to sleep, Tenma-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:15.44,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, as a result, I made some decent progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.31,0:18:18.90,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, I've been in a similar situation before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:23.20,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, that was when everything started.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:25.95,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.23,0:18:28.50,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From that moment on, you were...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:33.16,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think this is going a bit too far, Pervert-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:38.09,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've since worn sunglasses and grown a beard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:41.58,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've become a different person so I can move closer to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.34,0:18:43.90,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.90,0:18:46.98,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But this long drama will soon come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.53,0:18:51.69,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The finale of our relationship shall be a happy ending!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:55.08,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, this is no time to be getting excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:56.14,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Work, work...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:18:58.79,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can still eat lots more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.79,0:18:59.86,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,More food!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.39,0:19:02.80,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, she can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.43,0:19:12.75,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Harima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:16.75,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-N-No! I'm not that kind of guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:20.56,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T--Think about something else! Something else! Something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.56,0:19:23.51,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Harima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.79,0:19:25.88,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:28.82,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O--Oh crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:38.36,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be your opponent this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.40,0:19:45.11,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.74,0:19:59.95,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuurei-chan trudged off on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:03.59,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuurei-chan trudged on and on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:06.77,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ah, there are some flowers."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:09.48,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But there was no one behind her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:11.63,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ah, it's a shooting star."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:14.48,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, there was no one behind her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.43,0:20:18.53,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuurei-chan went home alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:22.20,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when she got home, there was no one there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:29.47,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even during mealtime, playtime, and cleaning time, she was alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.63,0:20:33.63,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Otama-chan, where did you go?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.63,0:20:37.84,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuurei-chan went to look for Otama-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:41.62,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She asked the worm on the flower,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.62,0:20:45.00,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Worm-san, Worm-san, where did Otrama-chan go?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:50.32,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yuurei-chan, I'm so hungry that I can't move."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.91,0:20:53.98,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll give you my food then."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:59.38,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"I saw Otama-chan gazing at the flowers."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:01.74,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Thank you, Worm-san."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.68,0:21:05.18,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She asked the twins by the seashore,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:09.49,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hey, hey, did the two of you see Otama-chan?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:13.38,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Look, we only have one toy."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.07,0:21:16.93,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll give you mine then."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.98,0:21:19.88,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Wow, thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:24.01,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Otama-chan was looking at the shooting stars over there."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:27.09,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Thank you, the both of you."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.11,0:21:32.95,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She walked and walked. Although everyone knows about Otama-chan, she is nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.04,0:21:36.77,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Where did Otama-chan go?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.57,0:21:41.31,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuurei-chan finally cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.42,0:21:47.16,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The tears fell one drop after another, forming a puddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.79,0:21:51.57,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Otama-chan, where did you go?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:01.13,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:10.30,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you love Harima-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.95,0:23:48.67,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, being a manga artist's assistant is really tough work!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.67,0:23:50.26,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Tsukamoto, didn't you just sleep the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.26,0:23:52.99,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of this kind of hard work that the finished manga is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.99,0:23:54.28,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The manga's not done though.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.28,0:23:56.11,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on School Rumble Ni Gakki:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.12,0:23:57.12,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sesame-- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.12,0:23:58.21,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.21,0:23:59.39,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a period!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.39,0:24:01.39,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,
